Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.gui.controllergui

Class PlayerViewController

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.client.gui.controllergui.PlayerViewController
All Implemented Interfaces:
GUIController, javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class PlayerViewController
extends java.lang.Object
implements GUIController, javafx.fxml.Initializable
This class represents the controller of the player view scene of the GUI application. Implements GUIController and Initializable interface. This class manage all the information to show to the user.
Author:
Stefano Fossati
